# Security (web APIs)

- **Owner/admin:** `requireOwner()` after `getAuthContext()`; never header-based impersonation.
- **Rate limits:** Use `lib/rate-limit.ts` / `lib/auth-rate-limit.ts` on abuse-prone public endpoints.
- **Stripe webhook:** Verify `stripe-signature` before mutations.
- **Downloads:** Validate signed tokens and entitlements in handlers (`lib/signed-download.ts`, `lib/entitlements.ts`).
